                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-65-off365 t18170702-65-cd366"></join>, one pair of boots, value 10s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18170702-65-victim550" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Bartlett
